{"tid":1634633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港澳門iPhone被「河蟹」  中華民國Emoji被消失，同Siri問天氣：中國台灣","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:44:05.000Z","uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"07b1bccf5a7964fde3f4fb0590bb226d055fd3ee","tid":1634633,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"中華民國國旗 Emoji 繼在 2017 年被發現消失於中國大陸版的 iOS，如今有人發現這個自我審查風潮再席捲香港、澳門。港澳用戶如把 iOS 更新至 13.1.1 或更新的版本，手機內原生 Emoji 鍵盤將無法輸入中華民國國旗，而且向 Siri 查詢天氣時，更會說出「中國台灣」。 <br />\n<br />\n以往港澳版 iOS，在 Emoji 鍵盤上亦可選擇輸入中華民國國旗，但在港澳用戶升級 iOS 13.1.1 之後，卻發現該項目被消失。<br />\n<br />\n有網民「Hikaru」發現 iOS 的程式碼當中，加入了「regionCode」的新程式碼，令區碼為「CN」以及「ZA」的 iOS 裝置都不能在 Emoji 鍵盤選擇中華民國國旗，另外所有 iOS 裝置如把地區設定為香港或澳門，亦不會選擇到中華民國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n不過有網民發現在英文輸入法當中輸入「Taiwan」，其關聯字功能會正常提出中華民國國旗的選項（用戶需先行開啟關聯字功能）。故此可知新版 iOS，仍能顯示中華民國國旗並靠這個特殊方法輸入。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Apple 亦對 Siri 平台有關「台灣」的稱呼更改為「中國台灣」。使用港版裝置查詢台灣天氣時，Siri 會回答中國台灣台北市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/07/emojiiphone/software/ios-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2Femojiiphone%2Fsoftware%2Fios-app%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=ec8d503a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/07/emojiiphone/software/ios-app/</a>"},{"pid":"ca5f2808d6698e65a0ba54d22e41dfa8f11822a9","tid":1634633,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Android 當立</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3bb5a4be3403bd1fe461920b04f84f99a06d8eb7","tid":1634633,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dd965262ce7c361245c47d9db5e6204a058c1f0","tid":1634633,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51038dc77567e3307a352e7863ad3544d0d7995e","tid":1634633,"uid":185872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"75659a1af17a7b1d076abddb1eb7b680e399736c","tid":1634633,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"正奶共西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣，香港"},{"pid":"850a6b16a9f335f16045eb781911d3297a65aa45","tid":1634633,"uid":275971,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsqQz7S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsqQz7S.jpg&h=d1f13684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c913eda78be8c3847e9ac907a8c6795ed99e1cab","tid":1634633,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母apple<br />\n仲assemble in china想食支那條水"},{"pid":"a95dc3fa60029cd8c0b13603c9b4c889c71ff483","tid":1634633,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:34:28.0